var student = Knob({ value: 85, angleOffset: 80, angleArc: 360, className: "review", lineCap: "round", thickness: 0.1, width: 180, height: 180, fgColor: '#fff', bgColor: primary }) document.getElementById('student').appendChild(student) }, []); const onChange = date => setDate({ date }); return (
